    <note>Chao(2) Zongke [7121] His father Gou's [3015] wife, Zhang(1) Shi, was a Jizhou, Juye resident, further evidence of the close connection between the two branches of Chao(2). Duanfu's [7122] grandfather, Zeng(1) Gong's [7364] father-in-law. Chao(2) Zongke was the FFBS son of Wang(2) Han's [1810] son-in-law, Chao(2) Zhongwei [3014]. Zongke's son-in-law, Yan(1) Ruoji [4080], was almost certainly a brother or cousin of Yan(1) Ruogu [2059] and Yan(1) Ruomeng [2060]. Zeng Gong, WJ, 45.16a-17a, 46.6b-8a. CBD, 3, 1951.</note>
